-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Diario AS</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+1</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Metr&oacute;poles</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+1</span></span></span></a><br></span></span><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">AS.com &ndash; &ldquo;O que precisa Brasil para classificar &agrave;s semifinais&hellip;&rdquo;</span> <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://as.com/futbol/internacional/que-necesita-brasil-para-clasificar-a-las-semifinales-de-la-copa-america-femenina-n/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Metr&oacute;poles</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+3</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Diario AS</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+3</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Metr&oacute;poles</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+3</span></span></span></a></span></span></span></p>', 'tinymce', '2025-07-22 05:41:20', 1, '687f4f04d4451.jpg', 52, 15, 12, '2025-07-22 05:41:20', '2025-07-23 12:29:10'),
(32, 'Terra gira mais rápido no dia 22 nesta terça feira: segundo dia mais curto já registrado', 'Em 22/07/2025, a Terra girou 1,34 milissegundos mais rápido, tornando esse o segundo dia mais curto já registrado — e exigindo ajustes no tempo atômico.', 'terra-gira-mais-rapido-no-dia-22-nesta-terca-feira-segundo-dia-mais-curto-ja-registrado', '<h3 data-start=\"228\" data-end=\"253\"><img src=\"https://www.brasilhilario.com.br/uploads/images/687f580d97515.jpg?1753176076896\" alt=\"imagem da terra\" width=\"826\" height=\"826\"></h3>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"228\" data-end=\"253\">Dia mais curto do ano.</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"331\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Nesta ter&ccedil;a-feira, 22 de julho de 2025, a Terra completou sua rota&ccedil;&atilde;o de cerca de 1,34 milissegundos mais r&aacute;pido que o padr&atilde;o de 24 horas, tornando-se o&nbsp;<strong data-start=\"151\" data-end=\"191\">segundo dia mais curto j&aacute; registrado</strong> desde 1974.</span></p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"338\" data-end=\"370\">Tend&ecirc;ncia incomum desde 2020.</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"372\" data-end=\"448\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Os cientistas apontam que desde 2020 o planeta tem registrado sucessivos dias mais r&aacute;pidos. O recorde ocorreu em 10 de julho, com 1,36 ms mais curto, seguido por 22 de julho (1,34 ms) e outra queda prevista em 5 de agosto (1,25 ms).</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"372\" data-end=\"448\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"455\" data-end=\"481\">Por que isso acontece?</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"483\" data-end=\"520\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Especialistas relacionam essa acelera&ccedil;&atilde;o a diversos fatores:</span></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"524\" data-end=\"601\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Mudan&ccedil;as no n&uacute;cleo fundido da Terra e redistribui&ccedil;&atilde;o de massa interna.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"604\" data-end=\"681\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Flutua&ccedil;&otilde;es causadas por mar&eacute;s lunares e atmosf&eacute;ricas, especialmente quando a Lua est&aacute; distante do equador.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"604\" data-end=\"681\">Impactos no nosso dia a dia.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"721\" data-end=\"760\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Apesar de impercept&iacute;vel ao cotidiano, esse desvio pode afetar sistemas que demandam precis&atilde;o extrema:</span></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"764\" data-end=\"783\">Rel&oacute;gios at&ocirc;micos.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"786\" data-end=\"827\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Rede GPS e telecomunica&ccedil;&otilde;es.</span></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"830\" data-end=\"854\">Transa&ccedil;&otilde;es financeiras.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"857\" data-end=\"919\">Infraestrutura cr&iacute;tica.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"926\" data-end=\"972\">Surge a proposta do \"leap second negativo\".</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"974\" data-end=\"1054\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Se a Terra continuar girando cada vez mais r&aacute;pido, pode ser necess&aacute;rio implementar o primeiro &ldquo;segundo bissexto negativo&rdquo; por volta de 2029 &mdash; ou seja, <em data-start=\"151\" data-end=\"160\">retirar</em> um segundo dos rel&oacute;gios at&ocirc;micos, o que nunca ocorreu antes.</span></p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1061\" data-end=\"1091\">Qu&atilde;o significativo isso &eacute;?</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"1093\" data-end=\"1173\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Embora 1,3 milissegundos pare&ccedil;a &iacute;nfimo, o ac&uacute;mulo pode gerar um segundo inteiro de diferen&ccedil;a por ano &mdash; o suficiente para comprometer sistemas sincronizados que operam em alt&iacute;ssima precis&atilde;o.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1093\" data-end=\"1173\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1180\" data-end=\"1201\">O futuro do tempo.</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"1203\" data-end=\"1283\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Especialistas afirmam que, apesar deste padr&atilde;o acelerado, a tend&ecirc;ncia de longo prazo segue sendo de dias mais longos &mdash; devido ao atrito gravitacional da Lua. Por&eacute;m, varia&ccedil;&otilde;es sazonais e recentes indicam que precisamos aprimorar os mecanismos de controle de tempo global</span>.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1203\" data-end=\"1283\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">O dia 22 de julho entrou para a hist&oacute;ria como o segundo mais curto j&aacute; registrado. Essas mudan&ccedil;as, embora m&iacute;nimas, refor&ccedil;am como nossa rela&ccedil;&atilde;o com o tempo &eacute; delicada &mdash; e que a ci&ecirc;ncia precisa acompanhar rigorosamente essas varia&ccedil;&otilde;es.</span></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1203\" data-end=\"1283\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 data-start=\"1867\" data-end=\"1876\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Fontes</span></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"1880\" data-end=\"1921\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Metr&oacute;poles &ndash; &ldquo;Terra gira mais r&aacute;pido nesta ter&ccedil;a, no 2&deg; dia mais curto da hist&oacute;ria&rdquo; (<a href=\"https://www.metropoles.com/ciencia/terra-girara-mais-veloz-no-dia-22\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-start=\"85\" data-end=\"171\">metropoles.com</a><br></span><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Times of India &ndash; &ldquo;Earth is spinning faster this summer: July 22 among the shortest days ever recorded&rdquo;</span> <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/etimes/trending/second-shortest-day-on-the-earth-2025-the-planet-will-spin-faster-than-usual-on-july-22-but-why-is-this-unusual-change-happening/articleshow/122829007.cms?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">The Times of India</span></span></span></a></span></span><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://www.metropoles.com/ciencia/terra-girara-mais-veloz-no-dia-22?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Metr&oacute;poles</span><span cl