k:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/starvation-and-despair-in-gaza-aid-is-just-another-injustice-0m597vqlv?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">The Times</span></span></span></a></span></span><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/liveblog/2025/7/22/live-israel-kills-60-in-gaza-hamas-says-working-on-truce-to-stop-famine?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Al Jazeera</span></span></span></a><br></span></span><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Reuters / AP &ndash; ONU ressalta mortes em filas de alimentos e for&ccedil;as israelenses</span> <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2025/07/20/gaza-aid-starvation-israel-un/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"